#. <section class="sutta" id="an10.70"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.70:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.70:0.2"
msgid "7. Yamakavagga"
msgstr "7. Pairs"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.70:0.3"
msgid "70. Dutiyakathāvatthusutta"
msgstr "70. Topics of Discussion (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an10.70:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, "
"Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery."

msgctxt "an10.70:1.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena sambahulā bhikkhū pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkantā "
"upaṭṭhānasālāyaṃ sannisinnā sannipatitā anekavihitaṃ tiracchānakathaṃ "
"anuyuttā viharanti, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"Now at that time, after the meal, on return from alms-round, several "
"mendicants sat together in the meeting hall."

msgctxt "an10.70:1.3"
msgid ""
"rājakathaṃ corakathaṃ mahāmattakathaṃ … pe … itibhavābhavakathaṃ iti vāti."
msgstr ""
"They engaged in all kinds of unworthy talk, such as talk about kings, "
"bandits, and ministers; talk about armies, threats, and wars; talk about "
"food, drink, clothes, and beds; talk about garlands and fragrances; talk "
"about family, vehicles, villages, towns, cities, and nations; talk about "
"women and heroes; street talk and well talk; talk about the departed; "
"miscellaneous talk; tales of land and sea; and talk about being reborn in "
"this or that state of existence."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli5.130"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an10.70:2.1"
msgid "“Dasayimāni, bhikkhave, pāsaṃsāni ṭhānāni."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are ten grounds for praise."

msgctxt "an10.70:2.2"
msgid "Katamāni dasa?"
msgstr "What ten?"

msgctxt "an10.70:2.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu attanā ca appiccho hoti, appicchakathañca "
"bhikkhūnaṃ kattā hoti."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant personally has few wishes, and speaks to the "
"mendicants on having few wishes."

msgctxt "an10.70:2.4"
msgid ""
"‘Appiccho bhikkhu appicchakathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā’ti pāsaṃsametaṃ ṭhānaṃ. "
"(1)"
msgstr "This is a ground for praise."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an10.70:3.1"
msgid "Attanā ca santuṭṭho hoti, santuṭṭhikathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā hoti."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant personally is content, and speaks to the mendicants on "
"contentment."

msgctxt "an10.70:3.2"
msgid ""
"‘Santuṭṭho bhikkhu santuṭṭhikathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā’ti pāsaṃsametaṃ "
"ṭhānaṃ. (2)"
msgstr "This is a ground for praise."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an10.70:4.1"
msgid "Attanā ca pavivitto hoti, pavivekakathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā hoti."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant personally is secluded, and speaks to the mendicants on "
"seclusion."

msgctxt "an10.70:4.2"
msgid ""
"‘Pavivitto bhikkhu pavivekakathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā’ti pāsaṃsametaṃ ṭhānaṃ. "
"(3)"
msgstr "This is a ground for praise."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an10.70:5.1"
msgid "Attanā ca asaṃsaṭṭho hoti, asaṃsaṭṭhakathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā hoti."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant personally doesn’t mix closely with others, and speaks to the "
"mendicants on not mixing closely with others."

msgctxt "an10.70:5.2"
msgid ""
"‘Asaṃsaṭṭho bhikkhu asaṃsaṭṭhakathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā’ti pāsaṃsametaṃ "
"ṭhānaṃ. (4)"
msgstr "This is a ground for praise."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an10.70:6.1"
msgid ""
"Attanā ca āraddhavīriyo hoti, vīriyārambhakathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā hoti."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant personally is energetic, and speaks to the mendicants on being "
"energetic."

msgctxt "an10.70:6.2"
msgid ""
"‘Āraddhavīriyo bhikkhu vīriyārambhakathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā’ti pāsaṃsametaṃ "
"ṭhānaṃ. (5)"
msgstr "This is a ground for praise."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an10.70:7.1"
msgid "Attanā ca sīlasampanno hoti, sīlasampadākathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā hoti."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant personally is accomplished in ethics, and speaks to the "
"mendicants on being accomplished in ethics."

msgctxt "an10.70:7.2"
msgid ""
"‘Sīlasampanno bhikkhu sīlasampadākathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā’ti pāsaṃsametaṃ "
"ṭhānaṃ. (6)"
msgstr "This is a ground for praise."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an10.70:8.1"
msgid ""
"Attanā ca samādhisampanno hoti, samādhisampadākathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā hoti."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant personally is accomplished in immersion, and speaks to the "
"mendicants on being accomplished in immersion."

msgctxt "an10.70:8.2"
msgid ""
"‘Samādhisampanno bhikkhu samādhisampadākathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā’ti "
"pāsaṃsametaṃ ṭhānaṃ. (7)"
msgstr "This is a ground for praise."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an10.70:9.1"
msgid ""
"Attanā ca paññāsampanno hoti, paññāsampadākathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā hoti."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant personally is accomplished in wisdom, and speaks to the "
"mendicants on being accomplished in wisdom."

msgctxt "an10.70:9.2"
msgid ""
"‘Paññāsampanno bhikkhu paññāsampadākathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā’ti pāsaṃsametaṃ "
"ṭhānaṃ. (8)"
msgstr "This is a ground for praise."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an10.70:10.1"
msgid ""
"Attanā ca vimuttisampanno hoti, vimuttisampadākathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā hoti."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant personally is accomplished in freedom, and speaks to the "
"mendicants on being accomplished in freedom."

msgctxt "an10.70:10.2"
msgid ""
"‘Vimuttisampanno bhikkhu vimuttisampadākathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā’ti "
"pāsaṃsametaṃ ṭhānaṃ. (9)"
msgstr "This is a ground for praise."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an10.70:11.1"
msgid ""
"Attanā ca vimuttiñāṇadassanasampanno hoti, vimuttiñāṇadassanasampadākathañca "
"bhikkhūnaṃ kattā hoti."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant personally is accomplished in the knowledge and vision of "
"freedom, and speaks to the mendicants on being accomplished in the knowledge "
"and vision of freedom."

msgctxt "an10.70:11.2"
msgid ""
"‘Vimuttiñāṇadassanasampanno bhikkhu vimuttiñāṇadassanasampadākathañca "
"bhikkhūnaṃ kattā’ti pāsaṃsametaṃ ṭhānaṃ. (10)"
msgstr "This is a ground for praise."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "an10.70:12.1"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, dasa pāsaṃsāni ṭhānānī”ti."
msgstr "These are the ten grounds for praise.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.70:12.2"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.70:12.3"
msgid "Yamakavaggo dutiyo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli5.131"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "an10.70:13.1"
msgid "Avijjā taṇhā niṭṭhā ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.70:13.2"
msgid "avecca dve sukhāni ca;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.70:13.3"
msgid "Naḷakapāne dve vuttā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.70:13.4"
msgid "kathāvatthūpare duveti."
msgstr ""
